title: 92/349/EEC: Commission Decision of 10 June 1992 amending Decision 91/643/EEC establishing a list of semen collection centres in the United States of America approved for the export to the Community of deep-frozen semen of domestic animals of the bovine species
header:
COMMISSION DECISION
of 10 June 1992
amending Decision 91/643/EEC establishing a list of semen  collection centres in the United States of America approved for the export to the Community of  deep-frozen semen of domestic animals of the bovine species
(92/349/EEC)
THE  COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
main_body: The Annex to Decision 91/643/EEC is hereby  replaced by the Annex to this Decision.
This Decision is addressed to the Member  States.
attachments:

Ray MAC SHARRY
